[
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1999年数学（一）真题解析",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            293,
            85,
            727,
            114
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "一、填空题",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            72,
            135,
            161,
            150
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1)【答案】 $\\frac{1}{3}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            72,
            157,
            216,
            185
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\left(\\frac{1}{x^2} -\\frac{1}{x\\tan x}\\right) = \\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{\\tan x - x}{x^2\\tan x} = \\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{\\tan x - x}{x^3}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            101,
            193,
            590,
            225
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n= \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {\\sec^ {2} x - 1}{3 x ^ {2}} = \\frac {1}{3}.\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            318,
            230,
            504,
            260
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2)【答案】 $\\sin x^2$ ",
        "bbox": [
            72,
            266,
            239,
            282
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】由 $\\int_0^x\\sin (x - t)^2\\mathrm{d}t\\xlongequal{x - t = u}\\int_x^0\\sin u^2 (-\\mathrm{d}u) = \\int_0^x\\sin u^2\\mathrm{d}u$ 得",
        "bbox": [
            101,
            287,
            673,
            316
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\frac {\\mathrm {d}}{\\mathrm {d} x} \\int_ {0} ^ {x} \\sin (x - t) ^ {2} \\mathrm {d} t = \\frac {\\mathrm {d}}{\\mathrm {d} x} \\int_ {0} ^ {x} \\sin u ^ {2} \\mathrm {d} u = \\sin x ^ {2}.\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            330,
            323,
            716,
            352
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(3)【答案】 $C_1\\mathrm{e}^{-2x} + C_2\\mathrm{e}^{2x} + \\frac{1}{4} x\\mathrm{e}^{2x}(C_1,C_2$ 为任意常数）.",
        "bbox": [
            72,
            360,
            561,
            388
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 特征方程为 $\\lambda^2 - 4 = 0$ ，特征根为 $\\lambda_1 = -2, \\lambda_2 = 2$ ",
        "bbox": [
            101,
            395,
            592,
            410
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "则 $y^{\\prime \\prime} - 4y = 0$ 的通解为 $y = C_{1}\\mathrm{e}^{-2x} + C_{2}\\mathrm{e}^{2x}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            101,
            416,
            487,
            432
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "令 $y^{\\prime \\prime} - 4y = \\mathrm{e}^{2x}$ 的特解为 $y_0(x) = ax\\mathrm{e}^{2x}$ ，代入得 $a = \\frac{1}{4}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            101,
            439,
            595,
            467
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故 $y^{\\prime \\prime} - 4y = \\mathrm{e}^{2x}$ 的通解为 $y = C_{1}\\mathrm{e}^{-2x} + C_{2}\\mathrm{e}^{2x} + \\frac{1}{4} x\\mathrm{e}^{2x}(C_{1},C_{2}$ 为任意常数).",
        "bbox": [
            101,
            475,
            747,
            502
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（4）【答案】 $\\lambda_{1} = \\lambda_{2} = \\dots = \\lambda_{n - 1} = 0, \\lambda_{n} = n$ ",
        "bbox": [
            72,
            510,
            462,
            526
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】方法一 由 $|\\lambda E - A| = \\left| \\begin{array}{cccc}\\lambda -1 & -1 & \\dots & -1\\\\ -1 & \\lambda -1 & \\dots & -1\\\\ \\vdots & \\vdots & & \\vdots \\\\ -1 & -1 & \\dots & \\lambda -1 \\end{array} \\right| = \\lambda^{n - 1}(\\lambda -n) = 0$ 得",
        "bbox": [
            101,
            529,
            799,
            609
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$\\mathbf{A}$ 的特征值为 $\\lambda_{1} = \\lambda_{2} = \\dots = \\lambda_{n - 1} = 0, \\lambda_{n} = n$ ",
        "bbox": [
            101,
            615,
            508,
            630
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "方法二 因为 $\\mathbf{A}^{\\mathrm{T}} = \\mathbf{A}$ ，所以 $\\mathbf{A}$ 可对角化，从而 $\\mathbf{A}$ 的非零特征值的个数与 $r(\\mathbf{A})$ 相同，",
        "bbox": [
            101,
            636,
            799,
            652
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $r(\\mathbf{A}) = 1$ 得 $A$ 只有一个非零特征值，",
        "bbox": [
            101,
            658,
            435,
            673
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "又因为 $\\operatorname{tr} A = n = \\lambda_1 + \\lambda_2 + \\dots + \\lambda_n$ ，所以 $A$ 的特征值为 $\\lambda_1 = \\lambda_2 = \\dots = \\lambda_{n-1} = 0, \\lambda_n = n$ .",
        "bbox": [
            101,
            677,
            867,
            694
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(5)【答案】 $\\frac{1}{4}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            72,
            701,
            216,
            728
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 令 $P(A) = p$ ",
        "bbox": [
            101,
            735,
            291,
            751
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "而 $P(A \\cup B \\cup C) = P(A) + P(B) + P(C) - P(AB) - P(AC) - P(BC) + P(ABC)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            101,
            755,
            828,
            771
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n= 3 p - 3 p ^ {2},\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            266,
            775,
            376,
            792
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "则 $3p - 3p^2 = \\frac{9}{16}$ ，解得 $p = \\frac{1}{4}$ 或 $p = \\frac{3}{4}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            101,
            798,
            471,
            825
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $P(A) < \\frac{1}{2}$ 得 $P(A) = \\frac{1}{4}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            103,
            834,
            363,
            861
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "二、选择题",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            72,
            869,
            161,
            883
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（1）【答案】 （A).",
        "bbox": [
            72,
            890,
            221,
            904
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 若 $f(x)$ 是奇函数， $F(x) = \\int_{a}^{x} f(t) \\, \\mathrm{d}t$ ",
        "bbox": [
            101,
            910,
            479,
            937
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "则 $F(-x) = \\int_{a}^{-x}f(t)\\mathrm{d}t\\frac{t = -u}{-a}\\int_{-a}^{x}f(-u)(-\\mathrm{d}u) = \\int_{-a}^{x}f(u)\\mathrm{d}u$ ",
        "bbox": [
            76,
            69,
            605,
            96
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n= \\int_ {- a} ^ {a} f (u) \\mathrm {d} u + \\int_ {a} ^ {x} f (u) \\mathrm {d} u = \\int_ {a} ^ {x} f (u) \\mathrm {d} u = F (x),\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            171,
            103,
            564,
            132
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "即 $F(x)$ 为偶函数，应选(A).",
        "bbox": [
            76,
            139,
            314,
            153
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2)【答案】 (D).",
        "bbox": [
            45,
            160,
            190,
            174
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $f_{+}^{\\prime}(0) = \\lim_{x\\to 0^{+}}\\frac{f(x) - f(0)}{x - 0} = \\lim_{x\\to 0^{+}}\\frac{1 - \\cos x}{x\\sqrt{x}} = 0;$ ",
        "bbox": [
            76,
            181,
            555,
            213
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nf _ {-} ^ {\\prime} (0) = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0 ^ {-}} \\frac {f (x) - f (0)}{x - 0} = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0 ^ {-}} x g (x) = 0,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            138,
            221,
            526,
            253
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为 $f_{+}^{\\prime}(0) = f_{-}^{\\prime}(0)$ ，所以 $f(x)$ 在 $x = 0$ 处可导，应选(D).",
        "bbox": [
            74,
            257,
            582,
            272
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(3)【答案】 (C).",
        "bbox": [
            45,
            279,
            190,
            293
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】显然 $S(x)$ 是以2为周期的偶函数，则 $S\\left(-\\frac{5}{2}\\right) = S\\left(-\\frac{1}{2}\\right) = S\\left(\\frac{1}{2}\\right)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            74,
            301,
            725,
            329
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "而 $S\\left(\\frac{1}{2}\\right) = \\frac{f\\left(\\frac{1}{2} - 0\\right) + f\\left(\\frac{1}{2} + 0\\right)}{2} = \\frac{3}{4}$ , 应选(C). ",
        "bbox": [
            76,
            338,
            524,
            381
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(4)【答案】 (B).",
        "bbox": [
            45,
            388,
            190,
            403
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 当 $m > n$ 时， $r(\\mathbf{A}) \\leqslant n, r(\\mathbf{B}) \\leqslant n$ ",
        "bbox": [
            74,
            410,
            431,
            424
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为 $r(\\mathbf{AB}) \\leqslant \\min \\{r(\\mathbf{A}), r(\\mathbf{B})\\}$ , 所以 $r(\\mathbf{AB}) \\leqslant n$ ",
        "bbox": [
            74,
            431,
            497,
            445
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "于是 $r(\\mathbf{AB}) < m$ ，即 $\\mathbf{AB}$ 为降秩矩阵，故 $|\\mathbf{AB}| = 0$ ，应选(B).",
        "bbox": [
            74,
            452,
            570,
            466
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（5）【答案】 (B).",
        "bbox": [
            45,
            474,
            190,
            488
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】因为 $X, Y$ 相互独立且 $X \\sim N(0,1), Y \\sim N(1,1)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            74,
            495,
            551,
            508
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "所以 $X + Y\\sim N(1,2)$ ，故 $P\\{X + Y\\leqslant 1\\} = \\frac{1}{2}$ ，应选(B).",
        "bbox": [
            74,
            518,
            551,
            544
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "三、【解】 $z = xf(x + y)$ 与 $F(x,y,z) = 0$ 两边对 $\\mathcal{X}$ 求导得",
        "bbox": [
            45,
            553,
            555,
            568
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l l} { \\frac {\\mathrm {d} z}{\\mathrm {d} x} = f + x \\left(1 + \\frac {\\mathrm {d} y}{\\mathrm {d} x}\\right) f ^ {\\prime},} \\\\ { F _ {x} ^ {\\prime} + F _ {y} ^ {\\prime} \\frac {\\mathrm {d} y}{\\mathrm {d} x} + F _ {z} ^ {\\prime} \\frac {\\mathrm {d} z}{\\mathrm {d} x} = 0,} \\end{array} \\right. \\text {即} \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l l} {- x f ^ {\\prime} \\frac {\\mathrm {d} y}{\\mathrm {d} x} + \\frac {\\mathrm {d} z}{\\mathrm {d} x} = f + x f ^ {\\prime},} \\\\ { F _ {y} ^ {\\prime} \\frac {\\mathrm {d} y}{\\mathrm {d} x} + F _ {z} ^ {\\prime} \\frac {\\mathrm {d} z}{\\mathrm {d} x} = - F _ {x} ^ {\\prime},} \\end{array} \\right.\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            247,
            575,
            741,
            641
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "解得 $\\frac{\\mathrm{d}z}{\\mathrm{d}x} = \\frac{(f + xf')F_y' - xf'F_x'}{F_y' + xf'F_z'}$ （ $F_{y}^{\\prime} + xf^{\\prime}F_{z}^{\\prime}\\neq 0)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            72,
            647,
            530,
            681
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "四、【解】令 $P(x,y) = \\mathrm{e}^{x}\\sin y - b(x + y)$ ， $Q(x,y) = \\mathrm{e}^{x}\\cos y - ax$ ，",
        "bbox": [
            45,
            687,
            654,
            702
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\frac {\\partial Q}{\\partial x} = \\mathrm {e} ^ {x} \\cos y - a, \\quad \\frac {\\partial P}{\\partial y} = \\mathrm {e} ^ {x} \\cos y - b,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            326,
            709,
            665,
            737
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nI = \\left(\\oint_ {L + \\overline {{O A}}} - \\int_ {\\overline {{O A}}}\\right) [ e ^ {x} \\sin y - b (x + y) ] d x + (e ^ {x} \\cos y - a x) d y,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            74,
            744,
            611,
            770
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "而 $\\oint_{L + \\overline{OA}}\\left[\\mathrm{e}^{x}\\sin y - b(x + y)\\right]\\mathrm{d}x + (\\mathrm{e}^{x}\\cos y - ax)\\mathrm{d}y = \\iint_{D}(b - a)\\mathrm{d}x\\mathrm{d}y = \\frac{\\pi}{2} (b - a)a^{2},$ ",
        "bbox": [
            74,
            778,
            795,
            811
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\int_ {\\overline {{O A}}} \\left[ e ^ {x} \\sin y - b (x + y) \\right] d x + \\left(e ^ {x} \\cos y - a x\\right) d y = - \\int_ {0} ^ {2 a} b x d x = - 2 a ^ {2} b,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            72,
            814,
            675,
            840
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故 $I = \\frac{\\pi}{2} (b - a)a^2 + 2a^2 b = \\left(\\frac{\\pi}{2} + 2\\right)a^2 b - \\frac{\\pi}{2} a^3.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            72,
            850,
            508,
            876
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "五、【解】 方法一 曲线 $y = y(x)$ 上任一点 $P(x,y)$ 处的切线为",
        "bbox": [
            45,
            883,
            597,
            900
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nY - y = y ^ {\\prime} (X - x),\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            297,
            905,
            471,
            921
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/1aa3b742c339223ec61e681acd2c86cf7224fbdb69f33ac6c06f5c657f19505c.jpg",
        "image_caption": [
            "五题图"
        ],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            714,
            814,
            923,
            915
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "令 $Y = 0$ 得 $X = x - \\frac{y}{y'}$ ，切线与 $x$ 轴的交点为 $Q\\left(x - \\frac{y}{y'}, 0\\right)$ ，垂足为 $T(x, 0)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            99,
            73,
            756,
            100
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "则 $S_{1} = \\frac{1}{2}\\cdot \\frac{y}{y^{\\prime}}\\cdot y = \\frac{y^{2}}{2y^{\\prime}}, S_{2} = \\int_{0}^{x}y(t)\\mathrm{d}t,$ ",
        "bbox": [
            99,
            106,
            481,
            138
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $2S_{1} - S_{2} = 1$ 得 $\\frac{y^2}{y'} -\\int_0^x y(t)\\mathrm{d}t = 1,$ ",
        "bbox": [
            99,
            143,
            423,
            172
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "两边对 $x$ 求导并整理得 $yy^{\\prime \\prime} = y^{\\prime 2}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            99,
            179,
            386,
            196
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "令 $y^\\prime = p$ ，则 $y^{\\prime \\prime} = p\\frac{\\mathrm{d}p}{\\mathrm{d}y}$ 代入得 $y p\\frac{\\mathrm{d}p}{\\mathrm{d}y} = p^{2}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            99,
            203,
            487,
            232
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为 $p \\neq 0$ ，所以 $\\frac{\\mathrm{d}p}{\\mathrm{d}y} - \\frac{1}{y} p = 0$ ，解得 $p = C_1 \\mathrm{e}^{-\\int -\\frac{1}{y} \\mathrm{d}y} = C_1 y$ ",
        "bbox": [
            99,
            237,
            601,
            269
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $y(0) = 1, y'(0) = 1$ 得 $C_1 = 1$ ，即 $\\frac{\\mathrm{dy}}{\\mathrm{dx}} - y = 0$ ",
        "bbox": [
            99,
            276,
            516,
            304
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "解得 $y = C_2\\mathrm{e}^{-\\int -\\mathrm{d}x} = C_2\\mathrm{e}^x$ ，再由 $y(0) = 1$ 得 $C_2 = 1$ ，故 $y = \\mathrm{e}^{x}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            99,
            313,
            632,
            336
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "方法二 曲线 $y = y(x)$ 上任一点 $P(x, y)$ 处的切线为 $Y - y = y'(X - x)$ ，",
        "bbox": [
            99,
            341,
            743,
            356
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "令 $Y = 0$ 得 $X = x - \\frac{y}{y'}$ ，切线与 $x$ 轴的交点为 $Q\\left(x - \\frac{y}{y'}, 0\\right)$ ，垂足为 $T(x, 0)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            99,
            366,
            756,
            392
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
